(5879,10126,"_et_pb_old_content","[et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" admin_label=\"section\" custom_padding=\"0px||0px|\" next_background_color=\"#000000\"][et_pb_row custom_padding=\"0px||0px|\" custom_margin=\"||0px|\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" module_id=\"blog-hero\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_post_title author=\"off\" comments=\"off\" featured_placement=\"background\" parallax_effect=\"on\" parallax_method=\"off\" text_orientation=\"center\" text_color=\"light\" text_background=\"on\" text_bg_color=\"#249ad6\" module_bg_color=\"rgba(255,255,255,0)\" module_id=\"blog-post\" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Before the redesign, BlueSky did an extensive review of Teatulias existing site \"]\n\n<h3 class=\"tertiary-callout\">Over the past few years, Teatulia, a premium single garden tea provider, had been successful in leveraging a content strategy that earned top rankings and solid traffic to their site. But, it was time for a redesign.</h3>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"BlueSky (we) was asked...\"]\n\nBlueSky (we) was asked to help Teatulia modernize their online store as they felt the site no longer reflected the caliber of their products and as a result, it was negatively impacting sales. With the site redesign, Teatulia wished to transition from a content-first mindset to a modern eCommerce site that integrated strong visuals, streamlined shopping and purchase flows and increased conversion rates from their Tea 101 landing pages.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Before the redesign, we did an extensive review of Teatulias existing site \"]\n\n<h3 class=\"tertiary-callout\">Before the redesign, BlueSky\'s creative team did an extensive review of Teatulias existing site.</h3>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"We noted several major UX issues...\"]\n\nA number of UX optimizations were identified that would improve the site\'s performance capabilities. Primary areas to address included a growing but disjointed navigation, a hard-to-find search bar, small product images and a non-responsive theme.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\" custom_padding=\"0px|||\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"No page was left untouched\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"tertiary-callout\">No page was left untouched during the redesign process.</h3>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"For aesthetic...\"]\n\nThe overall redesign theme was to present customers with a clean and modern design that would reflect the premium Teatulia brand and enable the shopping experience without unnecessary distractions. Letting the products speak for themselves was critical.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\" custom_padding=\"0px|||\"][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"No page was left untouched\"]\n\nTo address the growing list of categories, products and content pages within the existing site, the team chose to implement a well-organized custom megamenu with an area for promotional imagery. The search bar was super-sized and positioned front-and-center in the header, making it convenient for visitors to search from any page on the site.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://www.blueskytp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Screen-Shot-2017-05-02-at-11.49.00-AM.png\" show_in_lightbox=\"on\" use_overlay=\"on\" overlay_icon_color=\"#ffffff\" hover_overlay_color=\"rgba(36,154,214,0.75)\" max_width=\"100%\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#249ad6\" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\" custom_padding=\"0px|||\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_image src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/screencapture-teatulia-products-earl-grey-tea-16ct-eco-canister-htm-1492529428622-e1494266983186.png\" show_in_lightbox=\"on\" use_overlay=\"on\" overlay_icon_color=\"#ffffff\" hover_overlay_color=\"rgba(36,154,214,0.75)\" max_width=\"100%\" use_border_color=\"on\" border_color=\"#259ad6\" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"No page was left untouched\"]\n\nOur teamalso overhauled the product detail page by arranging content in an easy-to-read format. Another tactic was adding an award and certification ribbon next to the shopper actions to boost shopper confidence at a critical point in the path to purchase. Teatulia has an extensive Tea 101 content area where you can learn everything there is to know about tea. To bring some of that knowledge to shoppers, we incorporated helpful guides at the bottom of every tea category page to enhance the shopping experience and create a more informed and satisfied customer.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\" custom_padding=\"0px|||\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"No page was left untouched\"]\n\n<h3 class=\"tertiary-callout\">The Outcome</h3>\n\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"For aesthetic...\"]\n\nThe outcome of the redesign was an updated mobile experience, implementation of a desktop mega menu and the ability to display product information in a fashion not native to the template or backend. The BlueSky team leveraged solutions and features within the BigCommerce platform as well as customizations to acheive the new design.\n\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\" custom_padding=\"0px||0|\" padding_mobile=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#e8e8e8\" divider_position=\"top\" divider_weight=\"1px\" show_divider=\"on\" /][et_pb_code saved_tabs=\"all\"]<div class=\"medium-bstp-button button-diagonal button-center\"><a class=\"link_class\" href=\"/contact\" >Let\'s Talk</a></div>[/et_pb_code][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section bb_built=\"1\" prev_background_color=\"#000000\"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]"),
